title.narrative: Uttarakhand Decentralized Watershed Development II Project

description.narrative: The objective of the Project is to increase the efficiency of natural resource use and productivity of rainfed agriculture by participating communities in selected microwatersheds of the State of Uttarakhand.

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Interim Financial Reports | Description :Furnish to the Recipient and the Association, not later than forty-five(45) days after the end of each calendar quarter, an interim financial report. | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Project Internal Auditor | Description :Hire by no later than six (6) months after the Effective Date, aninternal auditor, under terms of reference acceptable to the Association. | Due Date :26-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement :Project Steering Committee | Description :Establish and thereafter maintain throughout the period ofimplementation of the Project, a state-level steering committee. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Project computerized accounting system | Description :Establish by no later than three (3) month after theEffective Date, and thereafter maintain throughout the period of implementation of the Project, a computerized accounting system. |Due Date :14-Oct-2014

Finance Agreement :WMD Multi-disciplinary teams at district level | Description :For each district involved in the Project,designate and thereafter maintain throughout the period of implementation of the Project, a multi-disciplinary team. | Frequency:CONTINUOUS
